{"tid":324640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖][又嬲又灰]隨街也是變態佬！！！","createTime":"2017-07-16T14:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T02:11:16.000Z","uid":99223,"like":17,"dislike":152,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2fc214deaffb7d35b7a2d96c29c2ecd67c384a2","tid":324640,"uid":99223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T14:44:04.000Z","msg":"真係又嬲又灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日係地鐵見到個變態佬(變唔變態見人見智啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n以下係圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/224103_319ef2031ab15bb8b37dbe76398586e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F224103_319ef2031ab15bb8b37dbe76398586e8.jpg&h=e88b186b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/224103_32a8f3f954e9af6482ea8642c39d4842.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F224103_32a8f3f954e9af6482ea8642c39d4842.jpg&h=e144d7fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:保護當事人所以blur咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始覺得佢完全係偷拍，好應該阻止呢種行為。但係岩岩想去阻止佢個陣，諗起其實連登大把呢d人，先勿理佢係上網揾d圖翻黎定係自己影。其實調翻轉頭，佢都係拎手機周圍影，唔通影港鐵大媽巴士阿叔個d又唔係偷拍，係網絡公審申張正義？再講又唔係影人裙底走光個d，當事人又冇做奇怪或者猥瑣的行為，到底誰正誰邪呢？<br />\n<br />\n好想知各位巴絲點睇<br />\n正評 - 緊係偷拍啦，即刻扑臭佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負評 - 又唔係影人裙底，由佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S. 條片比咗當事人，佢本人都冇做乜，不過想個阿伯del翻條片，可以點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dba4b7dc0953f302f036f48a304cf5fd1aaae7","tid":324640,"uid":99223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T14:45:56.000Z","msg":"話時話港鐵幫唔幫到手架？唔係就報驚"},{"pid":"d3be98363821f97dd9187ed4b4fad64078e7a951","tid":324640,"uid":16039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T14:49:03.000Z","msg":"俾人影嗰條友男人嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3006f6bc95fa11527bfc15b95a59b6926b3c98","tid":324640,"uid":99223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T14:53:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係又嬲又灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日係地鐵見到個變態佬(變唔變態見人見智啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n以下係圖<br />\n<br />\n利申:保護當事人所以blur咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始覺得佢完全係偷拍，好應該阻止呢種行為。但係岩岩想去阻止佢個陣，諗起其實連登大把呢d人，先勿理佢係上網揾d圖翻黎定係自己影。其實調翻轉頭，佢都係拎手機周圍影，唔通影港鐵大媽巴士阿叔個d又唔係偷拍，係網絡公審申張正義？再講又唔係影人裙底走光個d，當事人又冇做奇怪或者猥瑣的行為，到底誰正誰邪呢？<br />\n<br />\n好想知各位巴絲點睇<br />\n正評 - 緊係偷拍啦，即刻扑臭佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負評 - 又唔係影人裙底，由佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S. 條片比咗當事人，佢本人都冇做乜，不過想個阿伯del翻條片，可以點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔記得講事源<br />\n其實個條友一開始都奇奇怪怪，又扮錄音咁，個手機擺係個嘴到隋黎隋去，後面見到佢原來錄緊片，我又影住佢影人，到落車就比當事人。 我又算唔算係偷拍？"},{"pid":"fcf3c4c4896078e91a894a41dbe1d0ea3954f5a4","tid":324640,"uid":99223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T14:54:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾人影嗰條友男人嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係情侶黎 放大睇到 不過唔想影響到當事人所以cut咗"},{"pid":"814d9b060869f6bfabeb0342202f999aab51be8c","tid":324640,"uid":20522,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T14:54:50.000Z","msg":"你自己咪又係偷影緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d00f1b4707fa30c27aba029ecb251159cdea343","tid":324640,"uid":99223,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime